======================================================================
DOWNLOAD INSTRUCTIONS
======================================================================

To download a model:

1. Check available models:
   ollama list

2. Download a model:
   ollama pull phi3:latest
   ollama pull tinyllama:latest
   ollama pull qwen2.5:3b

3. Verify download:
   ollama list

4. Test the model:
   ollama run phi3:latest "Hello world"


======================================================================
STANDALONE TEST
======================================================================

To test phi3 standalone:
  python patricia_v4_3_multi_model.py test phi3

To test tinyllama standalone:
  python patricia_v4_3_multi_model.py test tinyllama
